    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十二月二十五日　昼",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1666.6666667000002,
          "startTime": 1.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "予定より遅くなっちゃった……時間、気を付けて\nおかないと……。あれ？　莉央さん……！",
      "startTime": 6.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.8000000318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、琴乃も来たのね\nまぁ、他にも来ていたみたいだけど",
      "startTime": 14.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8333333652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "花が、こんなに沢山……。三枝さんか、遙子さん？\nあ、{user}さんかな……",
      "startTime": 24.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.4000000318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "全員だったりしてね。他にもいそうだけど\nこんなことなら、最初からみんなで来れば良かったわ",
      "startTime": 32.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.7666666985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。大勢の方が賑やかになりますし、お姉ちゃんも\n喜ぶと思います。時間を合わせるのが大変そうですけど",
      "startTime": 40.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.9000000318
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そこが問題よね。私達、BIG4な訳だし\nクリスマスの日は特に忙しいもの。BIG4だから",
      "startTime": 51.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.0000000318
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "もう、あんまりお姉ちゃんに意地悪言わないで下さい\n……お姉ちゃん、後でお父さん達も来るからね",
      "startTime": 62.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.9333333652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "いいのよ。悔しがらせておけば。ろくに決着がつけられ\nなかったせいで、こっちは散々な目にあってるのよ？",
      "startTime": 70.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.0666682244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、そのおかげで、私達はもっと前に進めた訳だけど\nそれに、どうせまた、興味ないフリするんでしょうし",
      "startTime": 79.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.4666682244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうですね。「別に悔しくないもん」とか\n「まだトップに立ててないんだ？」とか、言いそうかも",
      "startTime": 91.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.4333359083
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "生意気にもほどがあるわ\n良かったわね、琴乃。お姉ちゃんに似なくて",
      "startTime": 98.0000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.700002575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、なんですか、それ\n莉央さん。改めて、BIG4おめでとうございます",
      "startTime": 106.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.9666692417
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがと。でも、それを言うなら、貴方もね\nおめでとう、琴乃",
      "startTime": 116.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.600002575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n随分、遠回りしちゃいましたけど",
      "startTime": 120.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.600002575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "言うじゃな～い。私の方が芸歴長いって知ってるくせに\n貴方が悩んでる時、力になれなかった当てつけ？",
      "startTime": 129.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.700002575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違います！　もぉ、意地悪ですよ\n莉央さんも莉央さんで、悩んでいたのは知ってますから",
      "startTime": 139.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.1666570347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、冗談よ。でも、これくらい言った方が\n面白いんじゃない？　賑やかな方が好きなんでしょ",
      "startTime": 147.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.6666570347
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん……。ふふ、じゃあ私も。お姉ちゃん\n私はもっともっと、成長するから。待っててね",
      "startTime": 159.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.033314546
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.133324178
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "それで、もしもいつか、その時がきたら\n――私とも、ライブバトルしてくれるかな",
      "startTime": 169.133324178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.699994437
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.1666737874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "ん、言うようになったじゃない。それでこそね\nあの子のことだから、向こうでもライブしてるだろうし",
      "startTime": 178.1666737874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "負けないように、私達も全力で進まないと\n琴乃も一緒だったわよね。まずは、この後の――",
      "startTime": 186.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 191.0666611036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスライブ！",
      "startTime": 191.0666611036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 191.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.8666600864
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
